<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:07:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登在加沙海岸附近的浮动援助运送码头是否总是沉在水中？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</link><description>这个耗资 2.3 亿美元的浮动码头在加沙海岸附近的两个月内仅运营了 28 天。更糟糕的是，6500吨物资中的大部分仍在等待国际机构领取，而不是到达巴勒斯坦人手中</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙地面上与以色列“幽灵部队”进行战斗，几乎不被人看到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</link><description>多域部队的以色列士兵在加沙行动中使用机器人、无人机和机密仪器。当我们陪同他们在加沙市中心执行任务时，有一件事明显缺席</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>在特拉维夫举行的重大和平活动之前，以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在美国各地集会要求停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</link><description>周日，包括以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在内的数百名抗议者在北美各地城市举行抗议活动，呼吁结束战争、返回人质并支持特拉维夫的“现在是时候”和平集会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管担心反犹太主义，但在加沙战争紧张局势中，LGBTQ 犹太人在纽约骄傲游行中找到了团结</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/despite-antisemitism-fears-lgbtq-jews-find-solidarity-at-nyc-pride-march-amid-gaza-war/00000190-6d95-d9ec-a19e-ef95228e0000</link><description>周日，数千名参与者和数百万观众挤满了纽约街头，其中包括挥舞着大卫之星骄傲旗帜、以色列人质的黄丝带和“自由巴勒斯坦”花车的 LGBTQ 犹太人。一位活动人士表示，“各个年龄段的酷儿犹太人都大胆而热情地参加了骄傲游行”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:16:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/despite-antisemitism-fears-lgbtq-jews-find-solidarity-at-nyc-pride-march-amid-gaza-war/00000190-6d95-d9ec-a19e-ef95228e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民事务部长奇克利表示，勒庞担任法国总统“对以色列非常有利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/diaspora-affairs-minister-chikli-says-le-pen-as-french-president-excellent-for-israel/00000190-6d11-d9ec-a19e-ef150a860000</link><description>这位极右翼的全国集会领袖因其政党历史性的反犹太主义而受到法国犹太团体无条件的反对。然而，以色列侨民事务部长对她的立场“印象深刻”，并补充说内塔尼亚胡似乎“持同样的观点”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/diaspora-affairs-minister-chikli-says-le-pen-as-french-president-excellent-for-israel/00000190-6d11-d9ec-a19e-ef150a860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列释放加沙希法医院院长；部长们猛烈抨击国防，辛贝特酋长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-director-ministers-slam-defense-shin-bet-chiefs/00000190-6d20-d499-a5bf-edbe84ad0000</link><description>这一决定激起了以色列部长们的愤怒，一些人要求撤换辛贝特的负责人。以色列监狱管理局和辛贝特发表了相互矛盾的声明来解释释放事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-releases-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-director-ministers-slam-defense-shin-bet-chiefs/00000190-6d20-d499-a5bf-edbe84ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府成员加剧了黎巴嫩爆发全面冲突的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/despite-risks-big-war-in-north-beckons-govt/00000190-6aad-d01f-abbe-7fad4b790000</link><description>对政府无法允许约 60,000 名以色列人返回黎巴嫩边境附近家园的批评越来越多。政府可能会试图寻求摆脱与真主党僵局的出路，并冒着爆发全面战争的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 03:36:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/despite-risks-big-war-in-north-beckons-govt/00000190-6aad-d01f-abbe-7fad4b790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布，以色列国防军士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-live/idf-18-soldiers-wounded-one-seriously-in-earlier-drone-explosion-in-northern-israel/00000190-6c13-db88-abb0-6e3729f00005</link><description>市议会表示，火箭弹击中了梅图拉的一栋房屋 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称妇女和青少年在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军杀害 ■ 西班牙要求加入国际法院对以色列的种族灭绝指控 ■ 加沙 Al-Shifa 医院院长在以色列被关押七个月后获释 ■ 以色列国防军：从加沙向以色列南部边境社区发射了 20 枚火箭弹 ■ BBC 报道：西岸巴勒斯坦人表示，以色列国防军士兵迫使他们登上军用吉普车引擎盖</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 03:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-live/idf-18-soldiers-wounded-one-seriously-in-earlier-drone-explosion-in-northern-israel/00000190-6c13-db88-abb0-6e3729f00005</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长们支持赋予议会权力挑选司法监察员的法案；总检察长反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</link><description>该法案将让候选人由立法者以无记名投票的方式批准，而不是由司法任命委员会批准。法院管理顾问批评该法案，称其是“旨在削弱司法部门权力的政权更迭运动的一部分”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-back-bill-giving-knesset-power-to-pick-judicial-ombudsman-ag-opposes/00000190-6a93-d90c-a7fc-7f9785f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准更改农业部名称 可能耗资高达200万谢克尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</link><description>在部长阿维·迪希特 (Avi Dichter) 要求更改后，该部现更名为农业和粮食安全部。以色列优质政府运动猛烈抨击了“投资数百万谢克尔进行无用的表面改变”的“妄想和不必要”的决定</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/cabinet-approves-changing-agriculture-ministrys-name-may-cost-up-to-2-million-shekels/00000190-6a7a-d9ec-a19e-ef7f380b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的民意调查很糟糕，但内塔尼亚胡的民意调查更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-30/ty-article/.highlight/bidens-polling-is-abysmal-but-netanyahus-is-even-worse/00000190-69a4-d9ec-a19e-efb59ab30000</link><description>在周四总统辩论后糟糕的民意调查结果中，美国总统乔·拜登可以稍稍安慰自己，因为至少有一位领导人更不被美国公民信任来领导他们</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-30/ty-article/.highlight/bidens-polling-is-abysmal-but-netanyahus-is-even-worse/00000190-69a4-d9ec-a19e-efb59ab30000</guid></item><item><title>数千名极端正统以色列人抗议征兵；正统派部长的汽车被投掷石块</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-against-haredi-conscription-ministers-car-pelted-with-stones/00000190-6a2d-d90c-a7fc-7f2de43a0000</link><description>数千名极端正统派男子涌上耶路撒冷街头，吹着号角，举着标语牌，反对高等法院的裁决，该裁决称他们必须应征入伍。 UTJ党部长Yitzchak Goldknopf开车穿过集会，抗议者向他的车投掷石块</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-against-haredi-conscription-ministers-car-pelted-with-stones/00000190-6a2d-d90c-a7fc-7f2de43a0000</guid></item><item><title>永远的新星节：以色列人跳舞纪念哈马斯的受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-festival-is-back-israelis-dancing-with-tears-in-their-eyes-in-tel-aviv/00000190-6a34-d407-aff0-6f3e057d0000</link><description>10月7日诺瓦节大屠杀受害者的感人音乐会一半是纪念一半是电子舞会</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-festival-is-back-israelis-dancing-with-tears-in-their-eyes-in-tel-aviv/00000190-6a34-d407-aff0-6f3e057d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 268 天：伊斯兰圣战组织称关键特工在西岸被以色列国防军杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-268-islamic-jihad-says-key-operative-killed-by-idf-in-west-bank/00000190-6a0d-d01f-abbe-7f0d27360001</link><description>巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织表示，其一名关键成员在以色列无人机袭击约旦河西岸时丧生 ■ 以色列国防军提高了对参与 10 月 7 日大屠杀但不属于哈马斯或伊斯兰圣战组织成员的巴勒斯坦人进行定点暗杀的门槛 ■ 阿拉伯联盟不再将真主党列为恐怖组织 ■ 战争进入 268 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-268-islamic-jihad-says-key-operative-killed-by-idf-in-west-bank/00000190-6a0d-d01f-abbe-7f0d27360001</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长批准为非犹太人保留“行政拘留”的法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-approve-law-that-would-reserve-administrative-detention-for-non-jews/00000190-69d7-d407-aff0-6fdfaa740000</link><description>拟议的法律规定，只有当该人属于旨在摧毁国家或伤害其公民的“恐怖组织”时，才允许行政拘留或未经审判的拘留。 10 月 7 日至 5 月 1 日期间，有 10 名犹太人被行政拘留，而阿拉伯人则有 2,733 名</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:53:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-approve-law-that-would-reserve-administrative-detention-for-non-jews/00000190-69d7-d407-aff0-6fdfaa740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准在内盖夫建造极端正统城市的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-authorizes-plans-for-ultra-orthodox-city-to-be-built-in-negev/00000190-698d-d90c-a7fc-7f8d9c9e0000</link><description>这座名为 Tilah 的新城市将容纳约 80,000 名居民。尽管遭到财政部的反对，但该计划仍在推进，财政部称与现有城市的扩张相比成本过高。环保组织和内盖夫市政府也反对该计划</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-authorizes-plans-for-ultra-orthodox-city-to-be-built-in-negev/00000190-698d-d90c-a7fc-7f8d9c9e0000</guid></item><item><title>为了生存，以色列现在必须袭击伊朗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-survive-israel-must-strike-iran-now/00000190-69e8-d01f-abbe-7de8d2260000</link><description>如果以色列证明无法使用常规武器摧毁伊朗核项目，那么它可能别无选择，只能诉诸非常规能力</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-survive-israel-must-strike-iran-now/00000190-69e8-d01f-abbe-7de8d2260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列工党与左翼梅雷茨合并为一党，称为“民主党”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-labor-party-left-wing-meretz-merge-to-be-called-the-democrats/00000190-69ec-d499-a5bf-e9febff20000</link><description>根据工党主席亚伊尔·戈兰和梅雷茨领导人托梅尔·雷兹尼克签署的协议，这不是技术性合并，而是创建一个全新的政党，该政党将作为一个单一实体继续前进</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:15:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israels-labor-party-left-wing-meretz-merge-to-be-called-the-democrats/00000190-69ec-d499-a5bf-e9febff20000</guid></item><item><title>拉宾暗杀喜剧和失控的阴茎吸引年轻的以色列人回到战时剧院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</link><description>特拉维夫卡梅里剧院的新一代剧团将幽默与震撼人心的内容结合在一起，并不回避政治主题。但加沙战争带来了不同的困境：导演说，外面的世界“太疯狂了，我们开始觉得我们的排练室是世界上唯一正常的地方”</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/theater/2024-06-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rabin-assassination-comedy-and-a-runaway-penis-lure-young-israelis-back-to-wartime-theater/00000190-59c5-d63a-a7b2-5ddf09e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称人质交易尚未完成，目标是回到谈判桌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</link><description>消息人士称，“双方之间的距离”很大，特别是在内塔尼亚胡发表有关“部分协议”的声明之后，而且调解员现在才试图重启谈判。另一位消息人士称，辛瓦尔对达成协议不感兴趣，他更希望北方局势升级而不是结束战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 13:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-source-says-hostage-deal-not-close-goal-is-to-get-back-to-negotiating-table/00000190-6942-d9ec-a19e-ef57f8cd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>